    "It is clear that the main topics are related to Romania, but one can see that climate change and renewable energy are often present in 2023's speeches.",
    "The fact is the consequence of the President's presence at meetings focused on sustainable energies, climate change mitigation, International Solar Alliance etc.",
    "Considering the whole corpus and the word distribution, it can be observed that the country's name constantly appears throughout the speeches (Figure 2).",
